pageType: final
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$darkBg"
elements:
  # 左上角几何水印（3%透明度）
  - elementId: final-watermark-tl
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 120, 120]
    shapeName: rect
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 0.5
      color: "#FFFFFF08"

  # 右下角几何水印（3%透明度）
  - elementId: final-watermark-br
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [1160, 600, 120, 120]
    shapeName: rect
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 0.5
      color: "#FFFFFF08"

  # 总结标题
  - elementId: final-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [240, 48, 800, 44]
    content:
      fontSize: 32
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>战略总结与行动号召</strong></p>

  # 铜色双线装饰 —— 上线
  - elementId: final-ornament-top
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [540, 104, 200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 0.5
      color: "$accent"

  # 铜色双线装饰 —— 下线（间距4px）
  - elementId: final-ornament-bottom
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [540, 108, 200, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 0.5
      color: "$accent"

  # ===== 3个核心战略要点 =====
  # 要点 1
  - elementId: point1-marker
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [180, 140, 12, 12]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: point1-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [204, 132, 800, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>全球化是集团未来三年<span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>最核心战略方向</strong></span>，海外营收目标 <span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>35%</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: point1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1060, 128, 120, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>¥50B</strong></p>

  # 要点 2
  - elementId: point2-marker
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [180, 186, 12, 12]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: point2-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [204, 178, 800, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>数字化与AI驱动效率革命，运营成本预计降低 <span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>40%</strong></span>，决策周期缩短 <span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>60%</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: point2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1060, 174, 120, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>3.2x</strong></p>

  # 要点 3
  - elementId: point3-marker
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [180, 232, 12, 12]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: point3-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [204, 224, 800, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>战略并购<span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>¥8B规模</strong></span>，补全供应链关键环节，释放协同价值 <span style="color:#B87333;"><strong>¥2B+</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: point3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1060, 220, 120, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>¥8B</strong></p>

  # ===== 分隔线 =====
  - elementId: divider-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [180, 280, 920, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#FFFFFF20"

  # ===== 待审议决议事项 =====
  - elementId: resolution-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [180, 300, 500, 32]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$lightCopper"
      fontFamily: "Georgia, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>待审议决议事项</strong></p>

  - elementId: resolution-1
    elementType: text
    bounds: [180, 344, 900, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>决议一：</strong>审批2025–2028年集团战略发展规划纲要</p>

  - elementId: resolution-2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [180, 380, 900, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>决议二：</strong>批准¥18.5B三年战略投资预算及并购授权</p>

  - elementId: resolution-3
    elementType: text
    bounds: [180, 416, 900, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>决议三：</strong>批准组织架构调整方案及全球化事业部设立</p>

  # ===== 底部信息区 =====
  - elementId: bottom-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [180, 520, 920, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#FFFFFF15"

  # Logo占位
  - elementId: final-logo
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [610, 548, 60, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#FFFFFF15"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#FFFFFF25"

  # 联系信息
  - elementId: contact-info
    elementType: text
    bounds: [340, 590, 600, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF88"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>XX集团战略发展部 · strategy@xxgroup.com</p>

  # 日期 + 机密标记
  - elementId: final-date
    elementType: text
    bounds: [340, 618, 600, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF55"
      fontFamily: "Inter, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>2025年X月 · 机密文件 · 仅供董事会成员传阅</p>
